Bahrain’s King Names New Head of Policies and Salaries, BNA Says

-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a
-- 
2011-04-04T14:12:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/bahrain-s-king-names-new-head-of-policies-and-salaries-bna-says.html
Bahrain’s King Hamad bin Isa Al Khalifa has appointed Adel Hajji Ibrahim as general director of
policies and salaries at the Civil Service Bureau, the Bahrain
News Agency reported today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vivian Salama in Abu Dhabi at 
 vsalama@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at  barden@bloomberg.net . 